name: カフカ - Kafka / Honkai: Star Rail - 崩壊スターレイル
description:
23th Release, カフカ - Kafka From Honkai: Star Rail - 崩壊スターレイル.

Put everything in Filter for seeing all images!

Click on Show more for Weight & Trigger recommendation, Also click on About This Version at Right Corner for more Info.

I know they are several Kafka Lora on Civitai, but i wanted to create mine and i tryed to be The most precise with the Best Quality Possible, with ONLY Original Art from Artist. (Pratically No GameScreepCaps & AI Image).

About this Lora:

  • Lora trained on 168+ Images at the max quality possible (Only Original Art 4K Images, Were used in the datasets) SFW+NFSW.

  • Trained at 768x Resolution for maximum Detail & Quality.

  • NAI Used, Work with Majority of the Anime Model's.

  • Work's greatly with Detail Tweaker Lora. (I Recommend to use it).

  • Can probably do Kafka in Realistic Cosplay.

For Prompts & Weight:

Flexibility is Ok. (See examples images).

About Trigger Words & Prompts: KafkaV4 (For Trigger) & for prompts just refer to examples images.

Weight recommended: 0.6-1.

Leave a Review & Share you're image in comments if you appreciate this Work :).

modelVersions.name: V4
modelVersions.description:
I pruned Purple hair, Purple eyes, so normally you don't need to put in prompt, but if they don't appear put: ((Purple hair, Purple Eyes)) prompt.

For Official Default Skin: Sometime the best weights is varying per model's, Like 0.7-0.8.

For Flexibility: for like clothes that don't exist put 0.6 - 0.8 Weight, See my Examples images for this.

Also if you don't want something to appear, put it in Negative Prompt.
